reviewText: I ordered this because my sunt was in one of the four movies.  Not the best quality but it was quite entertaing especially to see my aunt.
Love the oldies. Mix was a great actor!

The video quality is dreadful; so blurry that it resembles bad VHS tape.  The 8mm silent films I bought decades ago are superior to this DVD.  One of the two features has such extreme contrast that some scenes are washed out and titles card impossible to read.  If it were possible to rate this zero stars, I would.
